news/local/akron-renames-downtown-street-king-james-way-mayor-announces-during-lebron-james-celebration-30-000-people-attend-event-1.692548|archive-date=June 24, 2016|accessdate=June 23, 2016}}</ref>\n* Six-story commemorative banner in downtown Akron<ref name = \"Akron\" />\n* Honorary lockers at [[Ohio State]]'s football and basketball facilities<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/other/story/lebron-james-now-has-honorary-locker-at-ohio-state-090313|title=LeBron James has honorary locker at OSU|publisher=[[Fox Sports]]|accessdate=September 3, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cavaliers.247sports.com/Bolt/LOOK-LeBron-James-has-football-locker-at-Ohio-State-46662092|title=LeBron James has football locker at OSU|publisher=Cavaliers 24/7|accessdate=August 16, 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2008\n|''[[More than a Game]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Himself\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n|''[[Square Roots: The Story of SpongeBob SquarePants]]''\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n|''[[Trainwreck (film)|Trainwreck]]''\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n|''[[Smallfoot (film)|Smallfoot]]''\n| Gwangi\n|Voice role\n|-\n| 2021\n|''[[Space Jam 2]]''\n| Himself\n| Pre-production\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" | 2004\n|''[[My Wife and Kids]]''\n| rowspan=\"7\" | Himself\n| Episode: \"[[List of My Wife and Kids episodes#ep86|Outbreak Monkey]]\"\n||-\n| \n||-\n| September 29, 2007\n|''[[Saturday Night Live]]''\n|  | Himself\n| Episode: LeBron James/ Kanye West\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2009\n|''[[Entourage (U.S. TV series)|Entourage]]''\n| Episode: \"[[List of Entourage episodes#ep78|Give a Little Bit]]\"\n|-\n|''[[SpongeBob's Truth or Square]]''\n|TV movie\n|-\n| 2011\u20132014\n|''[[The LeBrons]]''\n|Lead role\n|-\n| 2015\n|''[[Survivor's Remorse]]''\n| Episode: \"[[Survivor's Remorse#ep15|Guts]]\"<ref>{{cite web|las